        "source_sentence": "「諸天當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307a27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸如來十力離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，四無所畏乃至十八佛不共法離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，如是乃至諸如來十力離即一切智智離，四無所畏乃至十八佛不共法離即一切智智離。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307a27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸天當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸三十二大士相離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，八十隨好離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，如是乃至諸三十二大士相離即一切智智離，八十隨好離即一切智智離。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸天當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸無忘失法離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，恒住捨性離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，如是乃至諸無忘失法離即一切智智離，恒住捨性離即一切智智離。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸天當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸一切智離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，道相智、一切相智離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，如是乃至諸一切智離即一切智智離，道相智、一切相智離即一切智智離。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸天當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b17_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸預流果離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，一來果乃至獨覺菩提離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，如是乃至諸預流果離即一切智智離，一來果乃至獨覺菩提離即一切智智離。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸天當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸菩薩摩訶薩行離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，如是乃至諸菩薩摩訶薩行離即一切智智離。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸天當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b25_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛無上正等菩提離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，如是乃至諸佛無上正等菩提離即一切智智離。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b25_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸天當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b28_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸一切智智離即布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多離，如是乃至諸一切智智離即諸佛無上正等菩提離。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307b28_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸天當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c01_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩聞說諸法無不遠離，其心不驚、不恐、不怖、不憂、不悔、不沈、不沒，當知是菩薩摩訶薩行深般若波羅蜜多。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c02_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告善現言：「何因緣故，諸菩薩摩訶薩於深般若波羅蜜多不沈、不沒？」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具壽善現白言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以一切法皆非有故、皆遠離故、皆寂靜故、無所有故、無生滅故，諸菩薩摩訶薩於深般若波羅蜜多不沈、不沒。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由如是等種種因緣，諸菩薩摩訶薩於深般若波羅蜜多不沈、不沒。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸菩薩摩訶薩於一切法，若能沈沒、若所沈沒、若沈沒時、若沈沒處、若沈沒者，由此沈沒皆不可得，以一切法不可得故。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩聞如是說，其心不驚、不恐、不怖、不憂、不悔、不沈、不沒，當知是菩薩摩訶薩行深般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩觀一切法皆不可得、不可施設，是能沈沒、是所沈沒、是沈沒時、是沈沒處、是沈沒者由此沈沒。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是因緣，諸菩薩摩訶薩聞如是說，其心不驚、不恐、不怖、不憂、不悔、不沈、不沒。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩能如是行甚深般若波羅蜜多，諸天帝釋、大梵天王、諸眾生主恒共禮敬。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告善現：「若菩薩摩訶薩能如是行甚深般若波羅蜜多，非但恒為諸天帝釋、大梵天王、諸眾生主共所禮敬，是菩薩摩訶薩亦為過此極光淨天、若遍淨天、若廣果天、若淨居天及餘天眾恒共禮敬。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c24_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩亦為十方無量、無數、無邊世界一切如來、應、正等覺現說法者恒共護念。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0307c28_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308a01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩能如是行甚深般若波羅蜜多故，則令布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多速得圓滿，亦令內空乃至無性自性空速得圓滿，亦令真如乃至不思議界速得圓滿，亦令苦、集、滅、道聖諦速得圓滿，亦令四念住乃至八聖道支速得圓滿，亦令四靜慮、四無量、四無色定速得圓滿，亦令八解脫乃至十遍處速得圓滿，亦令空、無相、無願解脫門速得圓滿，亦令極喜地乃至法雲地速得圓滿，亦令一切陀羅尼門、三摩地門速得圓滿，亦令五眼、六神通速得圓滿，亦令如來十力乃至十八佛不共法速得圓滿，亦令無忘失法、恒住捨性速得圓滿，亦令一切智、道相智、一切相智速得圓滿，亦令一切菩薩摩訶薩行速得圓滿，亦令諸佛無上正等菩提速得圓滿，亦令一切智智速得圓滿。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩能如是行甚深般若波羅蜜多，常為如來、應、正等覺及諸菩薩摩訶薩眾共所護念，速能圓滿一切功德，是菩薩摩訶薩當知行佛所應行處，亦正修行佛所行行故，此菩薩如佛世尊。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308a17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308a22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩其心堅固，假使十方殑伽沙等諸佛世界一切有情皆為惡魔，一一惡魔各復化作爾許惡魔，此諸惡魔皆有無量無邊神力，是諸惡魔盡其神力不能障礙是菩薩摩訶薩，令不能行甚深般若波羅蜜多，不證無上正等菩提。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308a22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308a28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩已得般若波羅蜜多方便善巧，達一切法不可得故。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308a28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩成就二法，一切惡魔不能障礙，令不能行甚深般若波羅蜜多，不證無上正等菩提。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為二？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、觀諸法皆畢竟空。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二、不棄捨一切有情。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩成就二法，一切惡魔不能障礙，令不能行甚深般若波羅蜜多，不證無上正等菩提。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為二？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、如所說悉皆能作。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二、為諸佛常所護念。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩能如是行甚深般若波羅蜜多，諸天神等常來禮敬，親近供養、請問勸發，作如是言：『善哉！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大士！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲證無上正等菩提，當勤住空、無相、無願。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大士！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩精勤住空、無相、無願，一切有情無依怙者能作依怙，無歸依者能作歸依，無救護者能作救護，無投趣者能作投趣，無洲渚者能作洲渚，無舍宅者能作舍宅，與暗冥者能作光明，與聾盲者能作耳目。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大士！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是住空、無相、無願即為安住甚深般若波羅蜜多，若能安住甚深般若波羅蜜多，疾證無上正等菩提。』",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩能如是住甚深般若波羅蜜多，便為十方無量、無數、無邊世界現在如來、應、正等覺處大眾中說正法時，自然歡喜稱揚讚歎是菩薩摩訶薩名字、種姓及諸功德，所謂安住甚深般若波羅蜜多微妙功德。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如我今者為眾宣說甚深般若波羅蜜多，於大眾前自然歡喜稱揚讚歎寶幢菩薩摩訶薩、頂髻菩薩摩訶薩等諸菩薩摩訶薩，及餘現住不動佛所，淨修梵行、安住般若波羅蜜多諸菩薩摩訶薩名字、種姓及諸功德，所謂安住甚深般若波羅蜜多微妙功德。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308b25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "現在東方殑伽沙等諸佛世界一切如來、應、正等覺，為眾宣說甚深般若波羅蜜多，於彼亦有諸菩薩摩訶薩淨修梵行，安住般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸如來、應、正等覺各於眾前，自然歡喜稱揚讚歎彼菩薩摩訶薩名字、種姓及諸功德，所謂安住甚深般若波羅蜜多微妙功德。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "南西北方四維上下殑伽沙等諸佛世界一切如來、應、正等覺，為眾宣說甚深般若波羅蜜多，於彼亦有諸菩薩摩訶薩淨修梵行，安住般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸如來、應、正等覺各於眾前，自然歡喜稱揚讚歎彼菩薩摩訶薩名字、種姓及諸功德，所謂安住甚深般若波羅蜜多微妙功德。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有菩薩摩訶薩從初發心修行般若波羅蜜多，漸次圓滿大菩提道，漸次圓滿甚深般若波羅蜜多，乃至當得一切智智，亦為十方殑伽沙等諸佛世界一切如來、應、正等覺說正法時，於大眾前自然歡喜稱揚讚歎是菩薩摩訶薩名字、種姓及諸功德，所謂修行甚深般若波羅蜜多微妙功德。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩能為難事，不斷佛種，饒益有情。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，具壽善現白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等菩薩摩訶薩為諸如來、應、正等覺說正法時，在大眾前自然歡喜稱揚讚歎名字、種姓及諸功德，為不退轉、退轉位耶？」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告善現：「有菩薩摩訶薩住不退轉位修行般若波羅蜜多，為諸如來、應、正等覺說正法時，在大眾前自然歡喜稱揚讚歎名字、種姓及諸功德。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0308c27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有菩薩摩訶薩雖未受記而行般若波羅蜜多，亦為如來、應、正等覺說正法時，在大眾前自然歡喜稱揚讚歎名字、種姓及諸功德。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309a01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，善現復白佛言：「此所說者是何菩薩？」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309a04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告善現：「有菩薩摩訶薩隨不動佛為菩薩時所行而學，已得安住不退轉地，是菩薩摩訶薩為諸如來、應、正等覺說正法時，在大眾前自然歡喜稱揚讚歎名字、種姓及諸功德。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309a05_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有菩薩摩訶薩隨寶幢菩薩摩訶薩、頂髻菩薩摩訶薩等所行而學，是菩薩摩訶薩雖未受記而勤精進行深般若波羅蜜多，亦為如來、應、正等覺說正法時，在大眾前自然歡喜稱揚讚歎名字、種姓及諸功德。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309a09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309a14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有菩薩摩訶薩行深般若波羅蜜多，於一切法無生性中雖深信解而未證得無生法忍，於深般若波羅蜜多雖深信解而亦未得無生法忍，於一切法畢竟空性雖深信解而亦未得無生法忍，於一切法皆寂靜性雖深信解而亦未得無生法忍，於一切法皆遠離性雖深信解而亦未得無生法忍，於一切法皆虛妄性雖深信解而亦未得無生法忍，於一切法皆是空性雖深信解而亦未得無生法忍，於一切法無所有性雖深信解而亦未得無生法忍，於一切法不自在性雖深信解而亦未得無生法忍，於一切法不堅實性雖深信解而亦未得無生法忍。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309a14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309a27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等菩薩摩訶薩亦為如來、應、正等覺說正法時，在大眾前自然歡喜稱揚讚歎名字、種姓及諸功德。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309a27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩為諸如來、應、正等覺說正法時，在大眾前自然歡喜稱揚讚歎名字、種姓及諸功德，是菩薩摩訶薩超諸聲聞、獨覺等地，定得無上正等菩提。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩行深般若波羅蜜多，為諸如來、應、正等覺說正法時，在大眾前自然歡喜稱揚讚歎名字、種姓及諸功德，是菩薩摩訶薩定當安住不退轉地，住是地已，速證無上正等菩提。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等，聞說如是甚深般若波羅蜜多，所有義趣無疑無惑、不迷不悶，但作是念：『如佛所說甚深般若波羅蜜多，其理必然定無顛倒。』",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人等，由聞般若波羅蜜多深生淨信，漸次當於不動佛所及諸菩薩摩訶薩所，廣聞般若波羅蜜多，於其義趣深生信解。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既信解已，當得住於不退轉地，住是地已，疾證無上正等菩提。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等，但聞如是甚深般若波羅蜜多，無疑無惑、不迷不謬、深生信解、不生誹謗，尚獲無量微妙善根，況能受持、讀誦、通利，依真如理繫念思惟，安住真如精勤修學！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人等速當安住不退轉地，疾證無上正等菩提，轉妙法輪度有情眾。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，具壽善現白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸法實性竟不可得，云何可說諸菩薩摩訶薩安住真如精勤修學，速當安住不退轉地，疾證無上正等菩提，轉妙法輪度有情眾？」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告善現：「如佛所化安住真如修菩薩行，速當安住不退轉地，疾證無上正等菩提，轉妙法輪度有情眾。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309b28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸菩薩摩訶薩亦復如是，安住真如修菩薩行，速當安住不退轉地，疾證無上正等菩提，轉妙法輪度有情眾。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具壽善現復白佛言：「如來所化都無所有，法離真如亦不可得，誰住真如修菩薩行？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰當安住不退轉地？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰證無上正等菩提？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰轉法輪、說何等法、度何等眾？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真如尚不可得，何況得有安住真如修菩薩行，速當安住不退轉地，疾證無上正等菩提，轉妙法輪度有情眾！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c08_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此若實有，必無是處。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告善現：「如是！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如汝所說。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來所化都無所有，法離真如亦不可得，誰住真如修菩薩行？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰當安住不退轉地？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰證無上正等菩提？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰轉法輪、說何等法、度何等眾？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真如尚不可得，何況得有安住真如修菩薩行，速當安住不退轉地，疾證無上正等菩提，轉妙法輪度有情眾！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此若實有，必無是處。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛出世若不出世，諸法法爾不離真如，廣說乃至不思議界。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "決定無有安住真如修菩薩行，廣說乃至度有情眾。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸法真如無生無滅，亦無住異少分可得。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若法無生無滅，亦無住異少分可得，誰住其中修菩薩行？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰當安住不退轉地？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰證無上正等菩提？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰轉法輪、說何等法、度何等眾？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此中一切都無所有，此若實有，定無是處。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但依世俗假施設有。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，天帝釋白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是般若波羅蜜多，最極甚深難信難解，諸菩薩摩訶薩行深般若波羅蜜多，雖知諸法皆不可得，而求無上正等菩提，欲為有情宣說正法甚為難事！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0309c28_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a02_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "決定無有安住真如修菩薩行、證得無上正等菩提、為諸有情說正法事，而諸菩薩摩訶薩行深般若波羅蜜多，觀一切法都無所有，於深法性其心不驚、不恐、不怖、無疑、無滯、不沈、不沒亦不迷悶，如是等事甚為希有！」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，善現語帝釋言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如汝所說。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a08_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸菩薩摩訶薩行深般若波羅蜜多，觀一切法都無所有，於深法性其心不驚、不恐、不怖、無疑、無滯、不沈、不沒亦不迷悶，如是等事甚希有者。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸菩薩摩訶薩行深般若波羅蜜多，觀一切法本性皆空，於此空中都無所有，誰可驚恐乃至迷悶！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故菩薩行深般若波羅蜜多，於深法性其心不驚、不恐、不怖、無疑、無滯、不沈、不沒、不迷、不悶，未為希有。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a14_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，天帝釋白善現言：「大德所說一切依空，是故所言常無罣礙。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a17_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如以箭仰射虛空，若遠若近俱無罣礙，大德所說亦復如是，誰能於中而敢抗對！」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a18_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第二分實語品第六十五之一",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，天帝釋白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我如是說、如是讚、如是記，為順世尊實語、法語，於法、隨法為正記不？」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，佛告言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝如是說、如是讚、如是記，諒順世尊實語、法語，於法、隨法誠為正記。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，天帝釋復白佛言：「希有！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大德善現諸有所說，一切依空、無相、無願，亦依四念住乃至八聖道支，亦依四靜慮、四無量、四無色定，亦依八解脫乃至十遍處，亦依苦、集、滅、道聖諦，亦依布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多，亦依內空乃至無性自性空，亦依真如乃至不思議界，亦依菩薩摩訶薩地，亦依一切陀羅尼門、三摩地門，亦依五眼、六神通，亦依如來十力乃至十八佛不共法，亦依無忘失法、恒住捨性，亦依一切智、道相智、一切相智，亦依一切菩薩摩訶薩行，亦依諸佛無上正等菩提。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310a27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，佛告天帝釋言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具壽善現住諸法空，觀布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多尚不可得，況有行布施波羅蜜多乃至般若波羅蜜多者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀四念住乃至八聖道支尚不可得，況有修四念住乃至八聖道支者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀四靜慮、四無量、四無色定尚不可得，況有修四靜慮、四無量、四無色定者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀八解脫乃至十遍處尚不可得，況有修八解脫乃至十遍處者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀苦、集、滅、道聖諦尚不可得，況有住苦、集、滅、道聖諦者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀內空乃至無性自性空尚不可得，況有住內空乃至無性自性空者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀真如乃至不思議界尚不可得，況有住真如乃至不思議界者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b20_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀空、無相、無願解脫門尚不可得，況有修空、無相、無願解脫門者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b21_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀極喜地乃至法雲地尚不可得，況有修極喜地乃至法雲地者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀一切陀羅尼門、三摩地門尚不可得，況有修一切陀羅尼門、三摩地門者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀五眼、六神通尚不可得，況有引發五眼、六神通者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀如來十力乃至十八佛不共法尚不可得，況有引發如來十力乃至十八佛不共法者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310b28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀無忘失法、恒住捨性尚不可得，況有引發無忘失法、恒住捨性者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀一切智、道相智、一切相智尚不可得，況有引發一切智、道相智、一切相智者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀一切菩薩摩訶薩行尚不可得，況有能行一切菩薩摩訶薩行者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀諸佛無上正等菩提尚不可得，況有能證諸佛無上正等菩提者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀一切智智尚不可得，況有能得一切智智者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀正法輪尚不可得，況有能轉正法輪者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀三十二大士相、八十隨好尚不可得，況有以此相好莊嚴身者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀無生無滅法尚不可得，況有能證無生無滅法者可得！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c12_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c13_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具壽善現於一切法住遠離住，住寂靜住，住無所有住，住無所得住，住空住，住無相住，住無願住。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c16_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具壽善現於一切法，住如是等無量勝住。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現所住無量勝住，比諸菩薩摩訶薩眾所住般若波羅蜜多甚深行住，百分不及一，千分不及一，百千分不及一，乃至鄔波尼殺曇分亦不及一。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c20_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c21_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "除如來住，是諸菩薩摩訶薩眾所住般若波羅蜜多甚深行住，於諸聲聞、獨覺等住，為最為勝、為尊為高、為妙為微妙、為上為無上、無等無等等。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c21_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是故，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c24_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩欲住一切有情上者，應住般若波羅蜜多甚深行住。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c24_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c26_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c26_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸菩薩摩訶薩住此住中，超諸聲聞、獨覺等地，證入菩薩正性離生，能速圓滿一切佛法，永斷煩惱習氣相續，能疾證得一切智智，得名如來、應、正等覺，能常利樂一切有情。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0310c26_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，眾中有無量無數三十三天，聞佛所說踊躍歡喜，各取天上微妙香花，奉散如來及苾芻眾。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，眾內六百苾芻從座而起頂禮佛足，偏覆左肩右膝著地，曲躬恭敬合掌向佛，瞻仰尊顏目不暫捨。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛神力故，各於掌中微妙香花自然盈滿，是苾芻眾歡喜踊躍得未曾有，各持此花而散佛上及諸菩薩。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既散花已咸發願言：「我等用斯勝善根力，願常安住甚深般若波羅蜜多微妙行住，聲聞、獨覺所不能住，速趣無上正等菩提，超諸聲聞、獨覺等地。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊知苾芻眾增上意樂趣大菩提定不退轉，即便微笑如佛常法，從其面門放種種光，青黃赤白紅紫碧綠金銀頗胝，遍照三千大千世界，其光漸攝還繞佛身，經三匝已從頂上入。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，慶喜既覩斯瑞歡喜踊躍，即從座起禮佛合掌白言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何因何緣現此微笑？",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛現笑非無因緣，唯願如來哀愍為說。」",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告慶喜：「是苾芻眾於未來世星喻劫中，當得作佛，同號散花如來、應、正等覺、明行圓滿、善逝、世間解、無上丈夫、調御士、天人師、佛、薄伽梵，彼佛壽量、所居國土、苾芻弟子一切皆同。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸如來、應、正等覺，初生出家及成佛後，隨所在處若晝若夜，常雨五色微妙音花。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a23_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是因緣故我微笑。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，慶喜！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a26_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩欲得安住最勝住者，當行般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩欲得安住如來住者，當行般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「慶喜當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人等，精勤修學甚深般若波羅蜜多，是善男子、善女人等，先世或從人中沒已還生此處，或從覩史多天上沒來生人中，彼於先世或在人間或居天上，由曾廣聞甚深般若波羅蜜多故，於今世能勤修學甚深般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311a29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慶喜當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311b05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來現見若善男子、善女人等能勤修學甚深般若波羅蜜多，於身、命、財無所顧者，定是菩薩摩訶薩也。",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311b06_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大般若波羅蜜多經卷第四百五十七",
        "from": "T07n0220_457:0311b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]